   174	/// TRACE_MATRIX § 3 orphan (TB-G G1.2-2 2026-05-11; Option B+ §3.2):
   175	/// acquire the single-writer chain-tape lease. On success returns a
   176	/// `LeaseGuard` whose drop releases the lease. On failure returns
   177	/// `LeaseError::AlreadyHeld` (live holder) or
   178	/// `LeaseError::HeadChangedSinceLastAcquire` (chain advanced under
   179	/// the caller — caller must rebase). Stale leases (holder pid dead)
