    38	//!    `QState::genesis()` plus any preseed; for the in-process test it
    39	//!    comes from `genesis_with_balances`).
    40	//!  - `task_end_snapshots` — `Vec<QState>` taken **after** each task's
    41	//!    last accepted L4 entry (one snapshot per `TaskContinuationEntry`).
    42	//!    In-process tests clone `Sequencer::q_snapshot()` after each
    43	//!    `bundle.shutdown().await`; the forward orchestrator (G1.2-6/7)
    44	//!    will derive these by `replay_full_transition` over the chain
    45	//!    entries from genesis up to each task's `end_chain_length`.
