   228	///    AND a prior snapshot was non-empty.
   229	///  - `reputation`: Reset if any snapshot's `reputations_t` is empty
   230	///    AND a prior snapshot was non-empty.
   231	///  - `pnl`: Reset if `(balances_total + collateral_total)` ever drops
   232	///    back to `initial.balances_total + initial.collateral_total` after
   233	///    a non-zero delta (i.e. the chain "unwound" its economic effect).
   234	///  - `autopsy`: Reset if `autopsy_capsule_total` ever decreases
