     8	//!
     9	//! For each task boundary recorded in the manifest, replays the chain
    10	//! via `replay_full_transition` (FC2-Boot canonical) to obtain the
    11	//! post-task `QState`. Calls `bind_persistence` to classify each of
    12	//! the six architect-required persisted fields (balances / positions /
    13	//! reputation / PnL / autopsy / model identity) as
    14	//! `Witnessed | Empty | Reset`. Writes the report as
    15	//! `<RUN_DIR>/PERSISTENCE_BINDING_REPORT.json`.
    16	//!
    17	//! Codex G1.2-6 micro-audit Q6 closure: gives the auditor a CAS-derived
    18	//! evidence artifact for the persistence-binding shape, instead of
    19	//! "Reset/Witnessed/Empty verdicts are not evidenced".
    20	//!
    21	//! Usage:
    22	//!
    23	//!   tb_g_persistence_report --run-dir <path>
    24	//!
    25	//! Exit codes:
